Looking at the income statement, I need to find the line item that represents financing costs. These are typically listed as "Financial Expenses" or similar terms.

In the provided income statement, I can see the line item "Financial Expenses" with a value of 372003.12 on 2024-02-05. This represents the financing costs incurred by the enterprise.

Therefore, the value of financing costs is 372003.12.
